{"type": "article", "id": 45030, "title": "一点也不意外，有人做了AirPods充电手机壳｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-09-10T23:11:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 43939, "name": "Onnit"}, {"id": 43940, "name": "Cramer-Krasselt"}, {"id": 18566, "name": "Daniel Arsham"}, {"id": 43941, "name": "Dinara Kasko"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 108, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170910200100U16y7k4cejfbtn3A.png", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>PodCase by Nova Technology</h3><p>苹果 AirPods 问世没多久，就有工业设计师为这副小巧的耳机专门开发了配件，我们之前介绍的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/42821.html\">小盒子</a>还兼备绕线、支撑手机的功能。最近，旧金山设计团队 Nova Technology 决定将配件做得一步到位，带来了这款充电外壳。PodCase 既满足了收纳耳机的需求，还能同时为它和 iPhone 充电。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/581404323/podcase-battery-case-for-your-iphone-and-airpods\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 89 美元起，电池容量为 2500 毫安时。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170910200138yzdkwVjaBEN0J2Cc.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170910200138Pi6wxrJgnoLfcRMH.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170910200138ZjNxuA0sCwgEBkFR.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709102001386eJ8sxRGmWNAbtSU.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Star Wars collection by Onnit</h3><p>以后去健身房打招呼或许可以用上《星球大战》系列中那句经典的“愿原力与你同在”了：美国健身公司 <a href=\"https://www.onnit.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Onnit</a> 最近推出了一套星战主题器械，包括三款黑色壶铃、瑜伽垫和重力球。重力球忠实还原了死星的外貌，而瑜伽垫则采用特殊工艺印制了韩·索罗的画像，尺寸更是1.8 米长的“等身版”。如果你感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.onnit.com/starwars/\" rel=\"nofollow\">专题页面</a>订购。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170910200210ijgkanX8AVZCxdRt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600244\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170910200210hzd3JTlHPAZXCanv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170910200210tLvQyrXUS6kcEpoF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600244\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Temp by Jack O’Farrell</h3><p>想成为只要戳一下或是看一眼食物就能知道几分熟的专业厨师？爱尔兰设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/jackofarre747c\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jack O’ Farrell</a> 带来的智能厨具 Temp 可以帮上忙。这套颇具未来感的黑色工具由一根勺子和配套的温度计构成，温度计的末端搭载了 LED 指示灯，既可以用在汤料中也能在确认肉类或蔬菜时单独使用。目前它还处于概念阶段，尚未投入生产。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170910200222JgBeAOlFxRc6k2GS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.778906\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170910200221joqb4sigGnTLPWad.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170910200221ZgJodRh1WMYx25CK.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562963\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170910200221pD3EQruFjqLHZ7i0.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.388889\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Naughty Bags by Cramer-Krasselt &amp; Diverse &amp; Resilient</h3><p>据统计，美国威斯康星州密尔沃基市的青少年怀孕率高达全国平均值的三倍。为此，当地的营销公司 <a href=\"https://c-k.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Cramer-Krasselt</a> 联手非盈利组织 <a href=\"https://www.diverseandresilient.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Diverse &amp; Resilient</a>，推出了一个名为 <a href=\"https://www.usenaughtybags.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Naughty Bags</a> 的公益安全套品牌，在怀孕率高的街区免费发放。和那些统一包装的品牌不同，他们一共设计了八款包装，借助风趣的插图和名称（例如 Papa Stopper、Snake Sweater），拉近与年轻人的距离。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170910200342mnp02kZqiL7dbSWP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170910200341BOAQZPdXMJcNpeDw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170910200341XSJBNRKzm2I1Vec6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170910200341Iq40bBJHYf12RsSG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170910200341K2ImWhnEcY1l98R6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lunar Garden by Daniel Arsham</h3><p>来自纽约的 <a href=\"https://www.danielarsham.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Daniel Arsham</a> 是一名色盲艺术家，他的早期作品大多以黑白灰为主。自 2016 年起，Arsham 开始在特制眼镜的帮助下让作品呈现出更丰富的颜色。他的最新作品是这件摆放在纽约凯迪拉克品牌中心“凯迪拉克之家”（<a href=\"http://www.cadillac.com/world-of-cadillac/cadillac-house.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Cadillac House</a>）内的装置艺术 Lunar Garden，一个被他重新解构的枯山水。除了尽头的一轮“满月”，整个装置都沉浸在粉红色的照明之中。据悉，它将展出至 11 月 5 日。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170910200236sntBOTa24C8gup1Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.272616\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170910200236csydAIotO3bDZRGk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623472\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170910200236csoPaZdiNuwL9gFh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>3D printing tarts by Dinara Kasko &amp; José Margulies</h3><p>还记得我们曾经介绍过的乌克兰<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/32609.html\">“建筑蛋糕师”Dinara Kasko</a> 吗？最近，她与来自迈阿密的艺术家 <a href=\"https://www.jmargulis.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">José Margulies</a> 合作，将他用塑料、铝和丙烯酸制作而成的雕塑装置转化为可食用的艺术品。这批蛋糕的层次和口味相当丰富，顶部的薄片让人不忍心下刀。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709102002473WtspH8Ky2gvDXuA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.734719\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170910200247l71WUYBjfATVDO9i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.772616\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170910200247Z9N0lSVBID2rmeyz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.573350\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170910200249aXt7DyuKx2HLhOCe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.759169\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}